= Background

The project combines #ASE scene assets, #EFM3D features, oracle #RRI labels, and VIN-style candidate scoring. Shared notation and glossary definitions are imported from the ARIA-NBV Typst shared modules, so thesis chapters can use symbols such as $#symb.oracle.rri$ and equations such as #eqs.rri.rri.
